{"tid":401972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[民主黨]胡志偉:各大學已表明反對「港獨」, 因此毋須作強硬遏止 ~","createTime":"2017-09-16T05:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T05:28:21.000Z","uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a1a1ef84f929ca6c54b8f3659bb306f1c58f527f","tid":401972,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:11:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://toronto.singtao.ca/2054192/2017-09-15/post-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8%E8%83%A1%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89%E7%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E3%80%8C%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E3%80%8D%E6%9C%89%E5%87%BA%E8%B7%AF/?variant=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftoronto.singtao.ca%2F2054192%2F2017-09-15%2Fpost-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589%25E7%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2588%25B0%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25B7%25AF%2F%3Fvariant%3Dzh-hk&d=2WDnxmZy%2BccQqbbXIAbz3k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a664ca9e\" target=\"_blank\">http://toronto.singtao.ca/2054192/2017-09-15/post-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8%E8%83%A1%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89%E7%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E3%80%8C%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E3%80%8D%E6%9C%89%E5%87%BA%E8%B7%AF/?variant=zh-hk</a><br />\n<br />\n多所大專院校近日雖然被貼上「港獨」宣傳品，但各大學已清楚表明不同意「港獨」。民主黨主席胡志偉表示，看不到亦不相信「港獨」在香港會有出路。<br />\n不過，他認為由於各大學已表明反對「港獨」，因此毋須作強硬遏止。他又指，張貼「港獨」宣傳品的人士，無非是希望尋求大眾的注意而已。"},{"pid":"bc8a8f618bc8c0b7f7cc25f2a3a72e07e3aa4113","tid":401972,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Z1X7u65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZ1X7u65.jpg&h=07b7bd76&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e3196ca063741af92148d2e7f9358e908e523f7","tid":401972,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:26:12.000Z","msg":"Myhk"},{"pid":"a5a82036cf3c614035aaf8d5b09854d6f8efc909","tid":401972,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:28:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Myhk</blockquote><br />\n堅定不移<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}